VPNId.name: VPNId
VPNId.description: The purpose of a VPN-ID is to uniquely identify a VPN. The Global VPN Identifier format is: 3 octet VPN Authority, Organizationally Unique Identifier followed by 4 octet VPN index identifying VPN according to OUI
VPNId.reference: Fox, B. and Gleeson, B., 'Virtual Private Networks Identifier', RFC 2685, September 1999.
